<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
<style>
    body{
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        border:0;
        font-family:  Tahoma, sans-serif;
    }
    .text-primary
    {
       color: rgb(66, 66, 190);
       font-size:2.2rem;
       text-align: center;
    }
    .card-text{
     background-color: #f1ebeba5;
     border-radius: 10px;
     padding: 20px;

    }
    .card-title
    {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .container
    {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap:wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        width:100%;

    }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="card-text m-4">

        <h2 class="card-title text-center">OTP VERIFICATION</h2>

        <hr/>
        <p class="">Hello,<%= email%></p>
        <p>We received a request to verify your email address. Please use the following OTP code to complete the verification process:</p>
        <p class="fw-bolder fs-4 text-center text-primary"><%= OTP %></p>
        <h3 class="fw-bold">This code is valid for 1 minutes.</h3>
        <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        <hr/>
       <div class="text-muted fs-4 text-center" style="text-align: center;">Thank you,<br/><span>
        FindFrnd</span>
       </div>
 </div>
</div>


 
</body>
</html>